data.message: Day 3 @ Gaomei Wetland for Platinum Members only
Good morning all DreamTrippers ,Please proceed to the Hospitality desk for registration

Hello Dreamtrippers,

Pls meet the representative at Arrival Hall upon arriving Taichung International Airport (09:00am - 18:00pm).
Hello! My name is Ivan ,The In-Destination Support of this trip. Hope you have a wonderful trip in Taichung, I will be waiting for you at the Lobby of Evergreen Laurel Hotel . See u there tomorrow .

Travel Tips
• A valid passport that expires at least 6 months after this trip is required.
• Contact your consulate for visa requirements.
• Bring your confirmation email, in case you are asked.
• Upon check-in you will be asked to provide proof of identification and a means in which to pay for incidentals incurred during your stay that are NOT included.
• Please do not forget to contact your credit card company to let them know you will be using it outside your state, for safety purposes.
• The best way to protect yourself from the unexpected is to purchase traveler's insurance.
• If you are traveling with any friends who you did not provide an email address for when you booked this DreamTrip - whether they are guests, member or non-members - please feel free to pass along this email to them as well.

Your trip includes 2 airport transfers:
December 21, 10 a.m., 1 p.m., 3 p.m. and 6 p.m.: From Taichung Airport to hotel.
December 24, 9 a.m., 11 a.m., 1 p.m. or 3 p.m.: From hotel to Taichung Airport.
To get free access to airport transfers, you must submit your flight information by December 4. 
https://roviadreamtrips.formstack.com/forms/1612tw8308_taichung_4

Hello DreamTrippers!
If you are traveling internationally to join this trip, please ensure that your passport is current and any required visa is obtained and valid. Many countries require passports and/or visas to be valid for a minimum of six months after the end date of this trip. It is your responsibility to obtain any required visas and other documentation prior to traveling. If you are unable to obtain a visa, the Cancellation Policy for this DreamTrip will apply.
